notes.text: Focus Sentinel. You dont get more than one healing absorb (Crushing Depths). Can Feign/pre-immune as needed.

Focus Sentinel  then chain pull.
This is a gauntlet.
LOS each Pack as needed here!

Stay grouped up and get knockback into a wall (Festering Shockwave)
Tank the boss around the room (spawn adds and puddles together) OOZES can be knocked back with direct damage abilities. (do not AOE)

CARE: Minions pulse damage! Be sure to have stuns and personals available.
Kill Totems and LOS Squid's Terrifying Vision

Stay stacked = make triangle patterns with 3 purple circles or place purple circles near existing puddles.  If you have a white beam on your stand then in purple puddles to "clean up" floor. https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dmIoeopSM8M
Spread equally around the Naz'jar Ravager ... this frontal is like the first boss in Freehold. You dont want anyone between you and the boss / you dont want anyone behind you.
